===Middlesbrough Legends===
These ten players were voted for by fans as part of a campaign with the ''[[Evening Gazette (Teesside)|Evening Gazette]]''.<ref name="Boro Legends">{{cite news|url=http://www.gazettelive.co.uk/boro-fc/boro-legends/ |title=Boro Legends |date=13 August 2007 |accessdate=1 August 2009 |work=[[Evening Gazette (Teesside)|Evening Gazette]] |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20080123154521/http://www.gazettelive.co.uk/boro-fc/boro-legends/ |archivedate=23 January 2008}}</ref>
<!--Please note: this is a specific group of ten players, as listed in the linked Evening Gazette article, and should not be changed. It contains only these: Camsell, Hardwick, Mannion, Clough, Hickton, Maddren, Mowbray, Slaven, Juninho and Southgate.-->
{{col-begin-small}}
{{col-3}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[George Camsell]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[George Hardwick]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Wilf Mannion]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Brian Clough]]
{{col-3}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[John Hickton]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Willie Maddren]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Tony Mowbray]]
{{col-3}}
* {{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Bernie Slaven]]
* {{flagicon|Brazil}} [[Juninho Paulista|Juninho]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Gareth Southgate]]
{{col-end}}

