===Football League 100 Legends===
The [[Football League 100 Legends]] is a list of "100 legendary [[association football|football]] players" produced by [[The Football League]] in 1998, to celebrate the 100th season of League football.<ref name="FL100">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/144986.stm |title=Sport: Football Legends list in full |publisher=BBC News   |date=5 August 1998 |accessdate=31 August 2007}}</ref>
{{col-begin-small}}
{{col-4}}
*
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Alf Common]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[George Camsell]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Steve Bloomer]]
{{col-4}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Wilf Mannion]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[George Hardwick]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Nobby Stiles]]
{{col-4}}
* {{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Graeme Souness]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Bryan Robson]]
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Paul Gascoigne]]
{{col-end}}

===English Football Hall of Fame===
The [[English Football Hall of Fame]] is housed at [[National Football Museum|The National Football Museum]] in [[Preston, Lancashire|Preston]], England. The Hall aims to celebrate and highlight the achievements of top English Footballers and Footballers who have played in England. These players appeared for or managed Middlesbrough at some point in their careers.<ref name="FLHOF">{{cite web|url=http://www.nationalfootballmuseum.com/halloffame.htm |title=Hall of Fame |publisher=[[National Football Museum]] |accessdate=31 August 2007 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20070811001406/http://www.nationalfootballmuseum.com/halloffame.htm <!--Added by H3llBot--> |archivedate=11 August 2007}}</ref>
{{col-begin-small}}
{{col-4}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Brian Clough]] ''(2002 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Paul Gascoigne]] ''(2002 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Bryan Robson]] ''(2002 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Viv Anderson]] ''(2004 inductee)''
{{col-4}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Wilf Mannion]] ''(2004 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Jack Charlton]] ''(2005 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Graeme Souness]] ''(2007 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Nobby Stiles]] ''(2007 inductee)''
{{col-4}}
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Terry Venables]] ''(2007 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Steve Bloomer]] ''(2008 inductee)''
* {{flagicon|England}} [[Malcolm Allison]] ''(2009 inductee)''
{{col-end}}

